oing as much damage as possible as fast as possible and the mage is king of this. Sure the wizards nuke harder, but the amount of damage our pet does often counters that. There are those few situations where it does not, but not often. That's my 2 cents. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ueraf@themagicianstower>Ueraf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#333333>(2/23/03 6:13:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=69.topic&index=43>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   err</span><hr size=1> i meant a game of chess, not chance... he he sorry<br>
